titles.title: To extend the temporary suspension of duty on cis-3-Hexen-1-ol.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

bill.summary: 4/26/2005--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend the suspension, through December 31, 2008, of the duty on cis-3-Hexen-1-ol.
